pot.com/2013/01/blog-post.html |title=言式法則：被汙名化的僵直性脊椎炎 |access-date=2013-01-24 |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121180459/https://yensrule.blogspot.com/2013/01/blog-post.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

